{"tid":2163084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民拒絕委任令香港成為支爆缺口， 從來冇人講過咁我講la","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:28:50.000Z","uid":335967,"like":26,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f8a4b3580be673e5e89df15a33462d3f9b4f0e3a","tid":2163084,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:41:55.000Z","msg":"1. 全體泛民拒絕人大委任加入臨時立法會(可以留番DQ 4)<br />\n<br />\n2. 臨時立法會成為<span class=\"red\">真空議會</span>，中共擁有絕對控制權<br />\n<br />\n3. 20/21財政年度通過<span class=\"red\">中部水域人工島前期研究5.5億撥款</span>(原本expect 19/20 立法年度通過，但拉布拉死咗)， 明日大嶼工程正式啟動<br />\n<br />\n4. 5年內通過<span class=\"red\">人工島填海工程1400億撥款，連同相關基建累計開支6400億</span>(18年估算，實際上肯定<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">超支至過萬億</span></span>)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">5. 庫房平均每年財政赤字超過1500億，財政儲備最遲10年內耗盡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">Q: 政府可以靠賣地收入支撐？</span><br />\nA: 賣地收入來自商業同私人樓市需求。 受政治因素同全球經濟衰退影響，加上外資企業逐漸撤離，商業需求將會下降(e.g. <span class=\"red\">8月中環甲級寫字樓空置率高達7.4%</span>)。香港投資環境不利，令私人樓市意欲下降。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">Q: 靠人工島回本？</span><br />\nA: 有錢人見香港投資環境不利都唔會喺香港買樓，得番啲新移民落嚟住公屋， 回條毛？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">6. 香港政府採取開源節流措施， 促成香港經濟崩潰:</span><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">A. 增加稅收</span>&gt;&gt; 直接打擊營商環境，增加中產移民，企業撤資意欲<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">B. 削減公共開支</span>&gt;&gt; 福利減少影響基層 ， 增加社會不穩同不滿情緒<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">C. 印刷港元增加財政供應</span>&gt;&gt; 直接同美元脫鉤，港元大幅貶值，導致物價指數大幅上漲， 對社會經濟民生造成全面打擊<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">D. 尋求中共協助</span>&gt;&gt; 中共要填過萬億，再加上本身對非洲各國嘅債務寬免，經濟雪上加霜。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">E. 發債</span>&gt;&gt; 撐中共啲窮國都自身難保，鬼得閒撐你<br />\n<br />\n7. 香港經濟全面崩潰，成為<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">支爆缺口，攬炒成功。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實泛民留任問題同國安法一樣: 國安法侵害自由，但通過咗就促進國際圍堵中共;泛民全體拒絕留任令中共為所欲為，但實際上<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">令香港置諸死地而後生。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d6c01da4d8db22af20287175804e5208b25b7d94","tid":2163084,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ae325dc8beb450e352f4f3cd918ae4d23d9a35","tid":2163084,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf2b66439245fd18c6c491b91710684f7ccf5ec","tid":2163084,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68b01de0c7ad750a828f10b1084e04ba6ff8267","tid":2163084,"uid":26846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:46:24.000Z","msg":"其實燒晒d錢 先係真攬炒"},{"pid":"1883560b716088e2481bcd3522bad9a6f66693f9","tid":2163084,"uid":362338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"睇完幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da66591e029c5ff4270e914224ead66e52fc429f","tid":2163084,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"有用post，推"},{"pid":"b30ca85d0457211c02592b4a794e6382c941e40d","tid":2163084,"uid":362338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"就係要睇佢連燒錢都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb40a9b0269ea93c62fa5832d5c5e0f1b17a291"